## 3️⃣ EXPORT THE WHOLE MAP STATE (5 min)

### a. Export as an image (using `html2canvas`)

Add the library (once) – you can load it from a CDN:

```html
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/html2canvas/1.4.1/html2canvas.min.js"></script>
```

Then add a **button** that captures the map view:

```html
<button id="exportMap" style="position:fixed;bottom:170px;right:10px;opacity:0.6;">
  📸 Export Map
